. Tasmiṃ kho pana dāne uttaro nāma māṇavo vāvaṭobyāvaṭo 
Note { id=56, line='492', referenceLine='73', original='byāvaṭo (sī. pī.)', type='auto', previous='. Tasmiṃ kho pana dāne uttaro nāma māṇavo vāvaṭo '
